ebkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-space; ">- Syntacti=
c analysis of non-structured written material;</div><div style=3D"word-wrap=
: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; -webkit-line-break: after-white-spa=
ce; ">- Identification of named entities arising from new means of communic=
ation;</div><div style=3D"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; =
-webkit-line-break: after-white-space; ">- Generation of words/phrases and =
language dynamism;</div><div style=3D"word-wrap: break-word; -webkit-nbsp-m=
